Program 2:
str = readline("Enter a string :")
res<- nchar(str)
cat("Total Length :",res)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Output:
> str = readline("Enter a string :")
Enter a string :naveen
> res<- nchar(str)
> cat("Total Length :",res)
Total Length : 6> 
